📊 Customer Segmentation – Business Insights
1. High-Value Customers (Cluster 1)
These customers have high total spending and frequent purchases
They contribute the major share of revenue
Likely loyal and engaged customers
💡 Business Actions:
Offer loyalty programs & exclusive discounts
Provide early access to new products
Focus on retention strategies
2. Low-Value Customers (Cluster 0)
Low spending and low purchase frequency
Minimal contribution to revenue
💡 Business Actions:
Use discount campaigns to activate
Avoid heavy marketing spend (low ROI)
Target with low-cost promotions (email/SMS)
3. Regular Customers (Cluster 2)
Moderate spending and purchase frequency
High potential to become high-value customers
💡 Business Actions:
Use personalized recommendations
Upsell and cross-sell strategies
Offer limited-time offers to increase engagement
